      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773198327674,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "* It is a communication patter where all processes (GPU) in a group participates simultaneoulsy. \n\n* In a distributed training, instead of one GPU sending data to other individually, all GPU coordinate\ntogether in single synchronized operation to move, recombine or distribute data across the entire group.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "* It is a communication patter where all processes (GPU) in a group participates simultaneoulsy. \n\n* In a distributed training, instead of one GPU sending data to other individually, all GPU coordinate\ntogether in single synchronized operation to move, recombine or distribute data across the entire group.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
